kind":"italic_en","text":"thrown at a boy"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so accord. to a copy of the T) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thrown by a boy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) on the authority of IAar. (T.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rimFA","text_ar":"رِمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[thus written in the M]: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramaA='N","text_ar":"رَمَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["T","K"]},{"entry_id":"n16737","headword_ar":"رَمِىٌّ","root":"rmY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to the male of the goat-kind, or mountain-goat, or of the gazelle, [and any male animal of the chase,] and likewise, without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", to the female,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maromiY~N","text_ar":"مَرْمِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thrown at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cast at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shot at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shot"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: but when they do not distinguish a male from a female, the word applied to the male and to the female is [↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramiy~apN","text_ar":"رَمِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",] with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[added"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liln~aqoli","text_ar":"لِلنَّقْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. to transfer it from the category of epithets to that of substantives]: or, accord. to Lh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramiY~N","text_ar":"رَمِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramiy~apN","text_ar":"رَمِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"are both applied, as epithets, to the female; but the former is the more approved: the pl. of the former [and of the latter also] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramaAyaA","text_ar":"رَمَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, TA.)       -A2-  Also, (M,) accord. to As,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqiY~N","text_ar":"سَقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e., (T, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cloud of which the rain-drops are large, and vehement in their fall,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the clouds of the hot season and of the autumn:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or, (M, K,) accord. to Lth, (T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small portions of clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"size of the hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat larger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but the approved explanation is that given by As: (T:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramoYN","text_ar":"رَمْىٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. var. thereof: (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aromiyapN","text_ar":"اَرْمِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, K,) like as that of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqiY~N","text_ar":"سَقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoqiyapN","text_ar":"اَسْقِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aromA='N","text_ar":"اَرْما=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, T, M, K,) [each, properly, a pl. of pauc.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramaAyaA","text_ar":"رَمَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["M","T","S","K","TA","Lth"]}]}}